    <p class="program-hero__acronym font-mono">LEADING A UNITED NEXT GENERATION CHANGE &middot; YOUNG ADULTS 18&ndash;26</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="program-quote">
  <div class="container">
    <blockquote class="program-quote__block">
      <p class="program-quote__text font-display">&ldquo;Your zip code is your starting line. Not your ceiling.&rdquo;</p>
