<section class="program-content">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="program-content__grid">
      <div class="program-content__main">
        <div class="program-content__section">
          <h2 class="program-content__heading font-display">What It Is</h2>
          <p>LAUNCH is a six-week economic empowerment program that attacks the gap between where young people are and where the economy needs them to be. Financial literacy, career navigation, entrepreneurship, and workforce entry&mdash;built for people the system was not built for.</p>
          <p>Participants leave with a financial plan, a professional network, and a clear path forward&mdash;not a certificate they can&rsquo;t use.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="program-content__section">
          <h2 class="program-content__heading font-display">The Problem</h2>
          <p>In Dallas-Fort Worth, youth unemployment in underserved communities runs two to three times higher than the regional average. Young people are told to &ldquo;get a job&rdquo; in an economy that was never designed to hire them first.</p>
          <p>LAUNCH does not fix young people. It confronts the systems that keep them locked out&mdash;and gives them the tools to break through anyway.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-content__aside">
        <div class="program-content__image">
