</section>

<section class="program-phases">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="program-phases__title font-display">Six Weeks. Real Ground.</h2>
    <div class="program-phases__timeline">

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">01</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Economic Reality</h3>
          <p>Map the economic landscape. Understand where the jobs are, where the money flows, and where young people are excluded.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">02</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Financial Literacy</h3>
          <p>Budgets, credit, debt, savings, taxes. The fundamentals no one taught you&mdash;taught by people who started where you are.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">03</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Career Navigation</h3>
          <p>Resumes, interviews, negotiations, networking. Not theory&mdash;live practice with real employers and hiring managers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">04</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Entrepreneurship</h3>
          <p>For participants building their own path. Business models, pitching, early revenue, and how to start without capital.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">05</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Network Building</h3>
          <p>Connect with mentors, employers, and peers who become your professional network for years&mdash;not just the program.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">06</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Launch Plan</h3>
          <p>Leave with a concrete 90-day plan: financial targets, career milestones, and accountability partners to keep you moving.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

